Session Summary — Chest Spawn System & Visual Themes
Chest Conveyer Spawn System ✅
Built the full chest spawning loop on the conveyer:

ChestRoller (ModuleScript) in ServerScriptService — RNG data module with chest tiers, aura weights, costs, and helper functions
ChestSpawner (Script) in ServerScriptService — handles the spawn → tween-in → wait → tween-out → respawn cycle
Chests spawn at ChestSpawn, glide smoothly along the X-axis, and stop dead-center on the conveyer
Uses each chest template's natural rotation + a 90° clockwise turn so the front faces the player
Auto-detects the conveyer belt surface via raycast; chest base hovers exactly 0.2 studs above it
Per-chest pivot Y calculation so different-sized chests all hover correctly

Skip & Grab Mechanics ✅

SkipChestBindable (BindableEvent) in ReplicatedStorage for server-to-server skip signals
ChestSkipServer (Script) on Plots.Plot1.ChestClick.ChestButton with a ClickDetector — clicking the button skips the current chest
ProximityPrompt on each spawned chest (key: E, "Grab Chest") — currently logs the grab to console; full grab→inventory logic still TODO
PrimaryPart property set on all 10 chest models in SwordPerChest

