Idle Animation System ✅

ChestAuraAnimator (LocalScript) in StarterPlayer.StarterPlayerScripts
Runs per-client, recursively scans workspace, animates every chest/aura GUI it finds
Per-rarity animation profiles: float amplitude, scale pulse, glow pulse, opacity flicker (Blaze), opacity pulse (Celestial/Golden), jitter (Toxic), jitter burst (Lightning), tilt (Corrupt), color shift (Corrupt)
Right-to-left gradient scrolling for Steel, Infinity, Lightning, Blood, Divine, Singularity
Doubled gradients (two cycles per stripe) eliminate visible seams when offset wraps

GUI Attachment ✅

ChestSpawner clones the matching ChestGUI template above each spawned chest
If an aura rolls, also clones the matching AuraGUI floating higher above
Both welded to chest's PrimaryPart so they follow the tween smoothly
Final positioning: ChestGUI at 3.5 studs above chest top, AuraGUI at 6.0 studs above (2.5 stud gap)
Both rotated 90° clockwise on Y-axis to face the player along the conveyer
TemplateName attribute stamped on clones so animator picks them up

